{"tid":2498813,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【接管黃馮】金管局研究替代付款機制 不經律師行戶口支付物業按揭貸款及大額款項","createTime":"2021-04-21T12:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T07:46:26.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22573729e72a2cc0bb91799303566a744c429680","tid":2498813,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"【接管黃馮】金管局研究替代付款機制 不經律師行戶口支付物業按揭貸款及大額款項<br />\n18:51 2021/04/21<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......署理財經事務及庫務局局長陳浩濂指，金管局正研究不經律師行戶口支付物業按揭貸款金額及其他大額款項的替代付款機制......<br />\n<br />\n......至今收到的意見顯示，有持分者表示支持，希望建議的機制能早日推出；亦有意見認為有關機制需要顧及物業交易可能涉及的不同場景和情況。金管局與銀行業界會考慮所得的意見，修訂方案和敲定具體的操作流程及細節。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2937950/%E3%80%90%E6%8E%A5%E7%AE%A1%E9%BB%83%E9%A6%AE%E3%80%91%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E4%BB%98%E6%AC%BE%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6%20%20%E4%B8%8D%E7%B6%93%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A1%8C%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%A7%E9%A1%8D%E6%AC%BE%E9%A0%85?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2937950%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%259B%25BF%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25BB%2598%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%2520%2520%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%258F%25AD%25E8%25B2%25B8%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A1%258D%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%25A0%2585%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=d55e84c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2937950/%E3%80%90%E6%8E%A5%E7%AE%A1%E9%BB%83%E9%A6%AE%E3%80%91%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A